              $475, PLUS 20% OF THE EXCESS OVER $4,750. 
Over $21,100 
            $3,745, PLUS 40% OF THE EXCESS OVER $21,100. 
      `(5) For taxable years beginning after 1999:  
                       `IF TAXABLE INCOME IS: 
                             The tax is: 
