              $380, PLUS 19% OF THE EXCESS OVER $4,750. 
Over $21,100 
           $3,486.50, PLUS 40% OF THE EXCESS OVER $21,100. 
  `(c) Unmarried Individuals: The tax schedule for an unmarried 
individual who is not a head of a household or a surviving spouse 
is-- 
      `(1) For taxable years beginning in 1996:  
                       `IF TAXABLE INCOME IS: 
                             The tax is: 
Not over $3,200 
                       19% OF TAXABLE INCOME. 
