<head>
<title>Campus Leader Volume 4, Issue 5</title>
<center>
<body background="/yaf/ground2.gif">
<img src="cl-logo.gif">
<h4>A Newsletter For Student Leaders From Young America's Foundation</h4>
<P>OCTOBER, 1996
