<TITLE>Family Research Council Washington Watch</TITLE>

<body bgcolor="#ffffff" text="#000000">

<CENTER><IMG SRC="/townhall/FRC/watch.gif" WIDTH=425 HEIGHT=125>
<p>
<H3>What's Happening In Washington?</H3>
</CENTER>
<HR SIZE = 3 WIDTH = 50%>
<P>The Family Research Council maintains a watch on Washington to ensure that citizens at the grassroots level are accurately and quickly informed of how public
policies, being formulated in the Legislative, Executive and Judicial branches of the federal
government, will affect families.  The Family Research Council is determined to expand its outreach through a wide variety of formats.  Timely information can
be gathered from these sources:
<UL> 
<ul type=ball>
<LI><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/books.html">Books and Special Reports</A>
<!-------<LI><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/congress.html">Congressional Testimony</A>--->
<LI><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/edfacts/edfacts.html"><i>Ed Facts</i></A> (weekly, updated 
Friday)
<LI><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/fampol/family.html">Family Policy</A> (6 issues annually)
<LI><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/hotline/hotline.html"><i>Legislative Hotline</i></A> (weekly, updated Friday)
<LI><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/letters/welcome.html">Monthly Letters from Gary L. Bauer</A>
<!------<LI><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/opinions.html">Opinions and Editorials</A>--->
<LI><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/policypapers.html">Policy Papers</A>
<LI><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/press/press.html">Press Releases</A><br>
<li><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/net/strttalk.html"><i>Straight Talk</i></a> (weekly 
television show)
<LI><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/radio/wwdaily.html.cgi">Washington Watch, The Daily Radio Commentary </A> (daily Monday to Friday)
<LI><A HREF = "/townhall/FRC/wwatch/wwnews.html">Washington Watch, The Newsletter </A> (10 editions annually)
</UL>
</ul>

<p><hr><p>

<center>
<a href="/townhall/FRC/images/navstrip.map">
<img src="/townhall/FRC/images/navstrip.gif" ismap border="0"></a>
<br>

