<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" background="/heritage/paperh.jpg">
<TITLE>BRYAN T. JOHNSON -- Heritage </TITLE>

<H3>BRYAN T. JOHNSON</H3>
<HR>
<B>POLICY ANALYST, INTERNATIONAL ECONOMIC AFFAIRS</B>
<P><IMG SRC="/heritage/staff/pics/johnson.gif" ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=10>
<P>
Johnson is co-author of Heritage's <a href="/heritage/index/">Index of Economic Freedom</a>, a global scorecard on the relative level of economic freedom in over 142 countries. A specialist on such issues as U.S.-Japan trade, industrial policy, and the detrimental effects of protectionism, Johnson previously served as Senior Editor and Writer at The Whalen Company, a consulting firm, and conducted research at Smick Medley International Inc. Johnson earned his B.A. at the University of Tampa.

<BR><HR WIDTH="30%"><p><p><CENTER><A HREF="/heritage/hbut.map"><IMG SRC="/heritage/hbut.gif" ISMAP BORDER=0></A></CENTER></BODY>
